# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User-specific
*.xcuserdatad
*.xcuserstate

## Swift Package Manager
.build/

## Playgrounds
*.app_contexts

## Derived Data
build/
DerivedData/

## Unit tests
*.xccheckout
*.xctestplan

## Various settings
*.xcscheme
!default.xcscheme
*.macruby
*.ipa
*.bundle
*.framework
*.dSYM

## CocoaPods
#
# It is a common debate whether to commit the Pods directory or not.
# https://guides.cocoapods.org/using/using-cocoapods.html#should-i-check-the-pods-directory-into-source-control
#
# Pods/
# *.xcworkspace

## Carthage
#
# It is a common debate whether to commit the Carthage/Build directory or not.
# https://github.com/Carthage/Carthage/blob/master/Documentation/Artifacts.md#build-artifacts
#
# Carthage/Build

## AccuRev
.accurev/

## Fastlane
#
# It is a common practice to have the fastlane directory committed to source control.
# However, you may want to ignore the 'report.xml' and 'screenshots' directory.
#
# fastlane/report.xml
# fastlane/Preview.html
# fastlane/screenshots
# fastlane/test_output

